[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1009","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0874","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"IIS 4.0 在处理包含 .HTR、.IDC 或 .STM 扩展名的文件请求时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标服务器发送特制的恶意请求触发该漏洞，成功利用后可导致拒绝服务或远程代码执行。该漏洞影响 Microsoft IIS 4.0 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0874"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:14.250","remediation":"升级到 IIS 5.0 或更新版本（如 IIS 6.0/7.0/8.0+），或在 IIS 4.0 中安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-019 对应补丁。作为缓解措施，在 IIS 管理器中删除 .HTR、.IDC、.STM 的 ISAPI 映射（如不需要），并启用 URLScan 工具过滤畸形请求。若系统已无支持，建议迁移至 Windows Server 2003 或更新系统。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ234905","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-048.shtml","http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD06081999.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-019","https://oval.cisecurity.org/repository/search/definition/oval%3Aorg.mitre.oval%3Adef%3A915","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19248"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1009.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1009.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1009.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0729","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0729.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0929","title":"Novell NetWare Novell-HTTP-Server HTTP GET 请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Novell NetWare 4.1/4.11 版本中集成的 Novell-HTTP-Server 及 YAWN Web 服务器存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标服务器发送大量 HTTP GET 请求，导致服务器资源耗尽无法响应正常请求，影响系统可用性。该漏洞影响 Novell NetWare 4.1/4.11 及相关组件版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0929"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.967","remediation":"升级 Novell NetWare 至 5.0 及以上版本（该问题已在后续版本修复），或在 Novell-HTTP-Server/YAWN 配置中限制单 IP 最大并发连接数，同时部署防火墙规则限制同一源 IP 的 HTTP 请求速率，防止大量 GET 请求耗尽服务器资源。如产品已停止支持，建议迁移至现代受支持的操作系统和 Web 服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0929"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0729.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0730","title":"Debian man-db zsoelim 本地符号链接漏洞","description":"Debian man-db 软件包中的 zsoelim 程序存在符号链接漏洞，本地攻击者可通过创建恶意的符号链接文件，诱使 zsoelim 在处理联机帮助页时将其解压输出重定向到任意文件，从而覆盖系统文件或提升权限。此漏洞利用条件为攻击者拥有本地账户权限，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害严重。受影响版本为 man-db 2.3.10 及更早版本。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0730"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:56.240","remediation":"升级 man-db 至 2.3.11 及以上版本，该版本已修复 zsoelim 在处理临时文件时的符号链接竞争条件。如无法升级，可限制本地非信任用户登录系统作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0730","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19243"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0307","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0307.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0713","title":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX dtlogin 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Compaq Tru64 UNIX 系统中的 dtlogin 程序在处理用户身份验证时存在权限提升漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 dtlogin 程序发送特制请求或利用其不安全的配置，成功利用此漏洞可将自身权限提升至 root 级别，从而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响 Compaq Tru64 UNIX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0713"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.077","remediation":"请升级至 Compaq Tru64 UNIX 最新可用补丁包（如 Tru64 UNIX 5.1B-6 及对应 Patch Kit），该漏洞在后续版本中已修复。如无法升级，建议移除 dtlogin 程序的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/dt/bin/dtlogin）以消除本地提权风险，或禁用 CDE 桌面环境服务替代为安全登录方式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-044.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0307.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0875","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1023","title":"Sun Solaris useradd 账户过期日期绕过漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 useradd 命令在解析 \"-e\"（账户过期日期）参数时，未能正确处理特定日期格式，当系统管理员或具有相应权限的用户使用某些非常规日期格式设置账户过期时间时，useradd 会错误地忽略或误解该设置，导致账户在过期后仍可正常登录系统。该漏洞影响 Solaris 7.0 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。攻击者需拥有本地账户并利用特定的日期格式参数即可绕过账户过期限制，获取非授权系统访问权限。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1023"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:32.613","remediation":"建议升级到 Solaris 8 或更高版本以彻底修复该问题。如无法升级，按 Sun 官方提供的解决方案替换 /etc/datemsk 配置文件，增加 %m/%d/%Y 等四位数年份格式（大写 %Y）使 useradd -e 能正确解析\"2000\"等四位年份，避免将 6/30/2000 误判为 2020 年。另外在创建账户后手动用 `logins -x` 验证到期日期是否正确，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92904175406756&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/426","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/2765cfa5d0fc39151c354509f5ba2b7abfdb61de/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1023","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1023.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/37da04e8698400cbfe936368ce494fc186159eb4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1023.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_110869.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mc67-m38f-vc3q/GHSA-mc67-m38f-vc3q.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/solaris7_x86_110870.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/426/info.html"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0875.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0706","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0706.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0775","title":"思科 IOS 千兆交换机路由器访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"思科（Cisco）运行 IOS 操作系统的千兆交换机路由器在处理访问控制列表中的 \"established\" 关键字时存在安全缺陷。远程攻击者无需认证即可利用该缺陷绕过 ACL 规则过滤，转发未经授权的网络数据包，导致网络访问控制失效。该漏洞影响多款思科交换机路由器产品，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0775"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.957","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至修复该漏洞的版本（如 12.0(5) 及更高版本），启用 CBAC（Context-Based Access Control）或 IOS 防火墙功能集进行有状态包检测替代 established 关键字。如无法升级，改用 reflexive ACL 或实施 TCP intercept 以验证完整 TCP 握手机制，同时在边界 ACL 中禁用不必要的入站 ACK 包。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0775"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0706.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1015","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1015.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1231","title":"SSH ssh 用户名枚举漏洞","description":"SSH 2.0.12 及部分其他版本在用户认证过程中存在用户名枚举漏洞。当客户端提供有效用户名时，服务器会提示输入密码并允许多次尝试；而输入无效用户名时仅提示一次即拒绝连接。远程攻击者可利用这一行为差异，通过遍历用户名并观察服务器响应，枚举目标系统上的有效用户账号，为后续暴力破解或针对性攻击提供信息支撑。该漏洞影响 SSH 2.0.12 及相关版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1231"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:59.880","remediation":"升级至 OpenSSH 3.0 及以上版本，该问题已在后续协议实现中得到修复。如无法升级，在 sshd_config 中设置 `MaxAuthTries 1` 限制单连接认证尝试次数，并启用 `LogLevel VERBOSE` 记录认证失败信息辅助审计。建议关闭密码认证 (`PasswordAuthentication no`)，改用公钥认证方式彻底阻断用户名枚举。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14758","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2276","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1231.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1231","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1231.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1231.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7g97-5hq7-x7mm/GHSA-7g97-5hq7-x7mm.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87557/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--0457d271-b4c6-4bb2-813d-1cf71d06fee5.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000668.txt","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/80b48aaf24cf1857bcadf6b9d454e9c0f7a850a5/1999/CVE-1999-1231.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1015.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0171","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0493","title":"Sun Solaris rpc.statd RPC 调用转发漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1 的 rpc.statd 服务存在远程 RPC 调用中继漏洞，远程攻击者可通过发送恶意的 SM_MON 和 SM_NOTIFY 命令将 RPC 调用转发至本地操作系统，进而利用该中继机制触发 automountd 等其他组件中的安全缺陷。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 2.5.1 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0493"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-06-07T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:30.887","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00186 提供的修补程序（Solaris 2.5.1 SPARC: Patch 103691-01, x86: Patch 103692-01）。如无法立即打补丁，可编辑 /etc/inetd.conf 注释掉 rpc.statd 行后重启 inetd 以禁用该服务，或在防火墙层面限制对 RPC portmapper（端口 111/tcp 和 111/udp）的入站访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91547759121289&w=2","http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/186&type=0&nav=sec.sba","http://www.cert.org/advisories/CA-99-05-statd-automountd.html","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-045.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/450","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19327"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0171.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1237","title":"Apache smbval SMB认证库 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库存在多处缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向使用该库的模块（如 Apache::AuthenSmb）发送特制的超长用户名或密码，触发缓冲区溢出，进而执行任意命令。CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。受影响的系统包括所有使用了受影响版本 smbvalid/smbval 库的 Web 服务器及应用，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1237"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:00.657","remediation":"立即停止使用已停止维护的 smbvalid/smbval SMB 认证库及 Apache::AuthenSmb 模块，迁移至 Apache 官方支持的 mod_authnz_ldap 模块通过 LDAP/LDAPS 协议对接 Active Directory 或 Samba DC 完成认证；如仍需 SMB 认证，可改用 Samba Winbind 结合 mod_authnz_ldap 实现，所有输入参数必须经过严格的长度校验与转义处理。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14384","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2272","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1237","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1237.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/openembedded/meta-openembedded/blob/e93799db0e7c7b23da8a00891403425ae7e87d7b/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65fj-56w9-gr9r/GHSA-65fj-56w9-gr9r.json","https://github.com/apache/calcite-avatica/blob/b8bc167268d0900087a24eecd150e8911a6225c0/src/main/config/dependency-check/suppressions.xml","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87828/info.html","https://github.com/anchore/cve-data-enrichment/blob/61a6f60f73f6727dfcef688b4834f32c678de1b5/data/anchore/1999/CVE-1999-1237.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0757","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0757.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0970","title":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD visadmin.exe 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Omnicron OmniHTTPD 1.1 及 2.0 版本中的 visadmin.exe 管理程序存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，仅通过向目标服务器发送精心构造的恶意 URL 请求，即可触发该程序在服务器上大量生成临时文件，迅速耗尽磁盘空间或系统资源，最终导致 Web 服务崩溃或无法响应正常请求。该漏洞影响运行 OmniHTTPD 1.1 与 2.0 Alpha 1 版本的 Windows 系统，CVSS 评分为 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0970"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:25.977","remediation":"OmniHTTPD 产品已停止维护，官方未发布补丁。建议立即停用 OmniHTTPD 并迁移至活跃维护的 Web 服务器（如 Apache httpd、Nginx）。临时缓解措施：在 Web 服务器或防火墙层面阻止对 /visadmin.exe 的外部访问请求，限制 Web 服务运行账户对临时文件目录的写入权限，降低被利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14311","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1808","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2271","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20304"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0757.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0757.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0757.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1688","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1063","title":"CdomainFree whois_raw.cgi 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"tags.<value>CdomainFree 2.4 的 whois_raw.cgi CGI 脚本中存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 fqdn 参数提交包含 shell 元字符的特制请求，在目标服务器上以 Web 服务器权限执行任意命令。该漏洞 CVSS 评分为 10.0，危害等级严重，攻击无需身份认证，可导致服务器完全受控。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1063"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:37.747","remediation":"由于 CdomainFree 2.4 已停止维护，建议立即删除或禁用 whois_raw.cgi 脚本，或在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面限制该脚本仅允许可信 IP 访问。同时在 CGI 参数处理中严格过滤 shell 元字符（; | & ` $ ( ) { } < >），并对 fqdn 参数实施白名单验证（仅允许域名合法字符），从根本上防止命令注入。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/14019","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/304","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/2251","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19242","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/297eb115816d3735806f02ee33bb4d2d53ecd5c6/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1063","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-1063.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2ed73314b4d66512efbb22e0644e615bc00001f2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/whois_raw.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/304/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1063.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1688.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1688.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0546","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0546.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0804","title":"Linux Linux内核 ICMP报文 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.2.x 内核的 ICMP 协议处理逻辑存在缺陷，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送包含异常类型、代码及畸变 IP 头长度的特制 ICMP 数据包，触发内核处理异常而导致拒绝服务。该漏洞无需认证即可远程触发，影响 Debian Linux 2.1、RedHat Linux 6.0、SuSE Linux 6.1 等发行版，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0804"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.527","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.4.0 或更高版本（该漏洞在 2.3.x 开发系列中已修复，2.4.0 正式版已彻底解决畸形 ICMP 包处理问题）。临时缓解措施：在网络边界防火墙配置规则，丢弃异常的 ICMP 类型和代码的报文，如禁止 ICMP 类型 13/14/17/18 等罕见类型的入站流量。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/302","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19241"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0546.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0499","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0772","title":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Compaq Insight Management Agent 及 Survey Utility 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标系统的 2301 端口发送超长字符串，触发服务组件缓冲区溢出，导致系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Compaq 多款服务器管理软件，危害等级中危，CVSS 评分 6.4。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0772"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-06-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:01.590","remediation":"建议升级至 Compaq 官方修补版本（Insight Management Agents 5.0 及以上版本）以修复长字符串导致的服务崩溃漏洞。如无法升级，可在防火墙策略中限制 TCP 2301 端口的访问来源，仅允许受信任的管理站 IP 连接。若业务不需要该服务，建议直接禁用 Compaq Insight Management Agent 服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0772"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0499.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0806","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0806.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0802","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"tags. Let me provide the final answer.<value>Internet Explorer 5 的收藏夹功能在处理网站提供的自定义图标时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可构造特制的畸形图标文件，当用户使用 IE 5 访问包含恶意图标的网页时触发缓冲区溢出，从而在用户系统上以当前用户权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows 95/98 平台上的 Internet Explorer 5 浏览器，CVSS 评分 7.6，危害等级高危。Microsoft 已在 MS99-018 安全公告中发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0802"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:05.283","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-018 提供的 Internet Explorer 5 更新补丁（KB231450），或升级至 Internet Explorer 5.01 Service Pack 2 及以上版本。当前 IE5 已停止支持，建议升级至 Microsoft Edge 或使用其他现代浏览器以避免更多安全风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231450","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-018"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0806.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0716","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0716.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0917","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer Preloader ActiveX 任意文件读取漏洞","description":"Internet Explorer 浏览器使用的 Preloader ActiveX 控件存在任意文件读取漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱导用户访问恶意网页，利用该 ActiveX 控件读取目标系统上的任意文件，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 Windows 系统中 Internet Explorer 浏览器支持的版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可实施攻击，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0917"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-05-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.540","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-018 提供的补丁（对应 KB231452），该补丁会彻底移除存在风险的 Preloader ActiveX 控件。如无法安装补丁，可在注册表中为 Preloader ActiveX 控件设置 Kill Bit（CLSID: {0000-0000-...}）以禁用该控件。鉴于 Internet Explorer 已停止安全支持，建议升级到现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome）作为根本解决方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ231452","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-018"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0716.toml"}]